snippet.title: The music of Tavern Talk | #indiegame #cozymusic #gamemusic #bardcore with  @FilippoBeckPeccoz
snippet.description:
Let us dive into the music of Tavern Talk with our bard Filippo Beck Peccoz. He'll shows you how he created the perfect atmosphere for our game!

Check out Filippos Youtube Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCJapPDbEW10dtc6OPJAwHTA

Please make sure to wishlist our game: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2076140/Tavern_Talk/

And follow our Kickstarter for more: https://tinyurl.com/TavernTalkKS
